# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Root-level Markdown is uncommitted by default: the planning/scratch docs at the repo root
# may carry private detail and must stay out of this OSS repo. The leading slash scopes
# the ignore to the repo root only, so Markdown in subdirectories (frontend/README.md,
# future docs/**) is tracked normally — no force-add dance. Shippable root docs are un-ignored
# explicitly below.
/*.md
!/README.md
